315
00:18:52,875 --> 00:18:54,625
MAN:
Keller is still in there!

316
00:18:58,333 --> 00:18:59,792
RIKER:
Let's move it!

317
00:18:59,792 --> 00:19:02,291
Out! Out! Out!
Let's go!

318
00:19:02,291 --> 00:19:04,500
Everybody move!
Everybody move!

319
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:06,166
