Evacuate immediately.

324
00:19:18,667 --> 00:19:21,041
Keller, can you
get to a Jefferies tube?

325
00:19:23,208 --> 00:19:25,709
Ensign Keller, answer me!

326
00:19:25,709 --> 00:19:27,375
You killed her.

327
00:19:28,375 --> 00:19:30,500
Keller is still in there!

328
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:33,000
Commander, radiation
levels are critical.

329
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,291
We've got to
seal it off.

330
00:19:34,291 --> 00:19:37,375
She was right
behind me.

331
00:19:37,375 --> 00:19:38,834
Bring down the door.

332
